  "detailed_description": "In Conrun you can race on one of many running tracks or you can compete in a virtual gym against AI by doing pushups, squats, crunches and other exercises.<br />\r\nYou really do workout.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou unlock each stage by winning the previous one.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEven if you lose, you will still get XP that unlocks cosmetic items. The more you do the more XP you will get.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame is divided in to 10 tiers. <br />\r\nDificulty level increases with each tier.<br />\r\nAmount of earned XP also increses with each tier.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt's time to build some muscles.",
